(1177, 200, 'team', 'The department is headed by Facilities Manager, assisted by the Assistance Facilities Manager. In addition to this, there is a group of supervisors namely Logistics Assistant, Maintenance Officer, Senior Security Officer, Head housekeeper and head driver who provide support in different sections. The team has housekeepers, drivers, security guards, maintenance staff and a receptionist.'),
