(3482, 432, 'internal_external_communications_story_0_description', '<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Pauline Hellen Mlogeni (Communications and Policy Coordinator)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Pauline has a Bachelor’s Degree in Journalism with 5 years’ postgraduate work experience. Pauline is a communications specialist with vast experience in Public Relations and Policy Engagement.</p>'),
