(19881, 3094, 'governance', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">MLW is an affiliate of the College of Medicine (CoM). Legally it is part of the College of Medicine. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are four key management groups in MLW (Senior Management Team [SMT] , Research Strategy Group [RSG], Research Support Units [RSUs] and Operations Heads of Department [HODs]) which manage MLW under the overall governance of the Executive Committee in the structure below:</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-3091 aligncenter\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/governance.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"288\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These key groups support each other through a framework of monthly, quarterly and bi-annual meetings.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Scientific strategy</h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Director is assisted in delivering the 2 major Programmes, Strategic Initiative, Training</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and Policy elements of the scientific strategy by Senior Scientists within each Programme, Research Group Heads, Training and Policy leads. The </span><b>Research Strategy Group </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(RSG) reviews</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and accepts all new projects. RSG includes the Director, Deputy Director, Chief Operating Officer, Heads of Groups including Associate Director, Heads of Research Support Units </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Clinical, Laboratories, Data &amp; Statistics). A major measure of each Research Group strength </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and value is demonstrated by provision of specific expert oversight and quality assurance to </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">particular Core Facilities. The particular areas of management and quality assurance for each Group within the Programme.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are 11 Operational Departments (Finance, HR, IT, Data, Laboratory, Clinical Services, </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Health and Safety, Chikwawa and other Field Sites, Science Communications, Facilities). </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These are each headed by a Departmental Head who takes full responsibility for their </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">department. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
