(20031, 3111, 'details', 'We exist to provide operational field sites support for research projects in urban and rural field sites.\r\n\r\nWe provide the following services:\r\n\r\nManage common cost issues among studies in the field sites.\r\n\r\nDevelop and maintain an efficient and effective relationship with different hosting institutions and other external stakeholders in the field sites.\r\n\r\nManage infrastructure needs of projects.\r\n\r\nFacilitate communication and coordination between Field Sites Focal Persons and MLW departments/projects.\r\n\r\nDevelop and maintain field sites SOPs and policies to ensure good practice\r\n\r\nField sites record management.\r\n\r\nField sites strategic planning and project management\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
