(9, 1, '2020-01-20 07:10:50', '2020-01-20 07:10:50', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our vision</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MLW has a vision of science driving health and wellbeing in Malawi.&nbsp; This is bold, ambitious, and challenging as Malawi is faced with challenges related to population density, climate change and environmental degradation, nutrition, education, and endemic diseases including HIV, TB, and malaria.&nbsp; MLW scientists have courage, commitment, energy, and belief – with these combined with excellent funding, facilities, and partnerships, we achieve great things.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our mission</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The MLW mission is to conduct high quality research to improve health and to train the next generation of researchers.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Research is  nurtured in six Themes – </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/population-health/\">Population Health</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/social-sciences/\"> Social Sciences </a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/maternal-neonatal-and-child-health-theme/\">Maternal, Neonatal and Child Health,</a> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/vaccine-implementation-and-impact/\">Vaccines</a> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/clinical-and-experimental-medicine/\">Clinical and Experimental Medicine </a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/infection-biology/\"> Infection Biology.&nbsp;</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These Themes catalyse the interactions between our 15 Research Groups, six Associate Research Groups and three Research Support Units.&nbsp; Themes are a natural transition from the previous two large programme aims which were (1) To prevent deaths in hospital and (2) to prevent disease in the community.&nbsp; The change has been driven by growth, diversity and the ideas generated by a new generation of leaders.&nbsp; Training in MLW is from junior scientist to Group Head and from operations staff recruit to Department Head. Nine of the Research Group Heads as well as the Director were previously trainees at MLW.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Best wishes</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2020-11-24 08:25:29', '2020-11-24 08:25:29', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
