(45, 1, '2020-01-20 12:13:27', '2020-01-20 12:13:27', 'Medical anthropologist with a background in HIV interventions, risk perception and behaviour, microbicides and the acceptability of medical research. Also has significant experience in mixed methods public health research in resource-poor contexts, particularly in East and Southern Africa. Current research interests include treatment seeking for meningitis and other febrile illness, the social impacts of introducing and scaling up self-testing for HIV in Malawi and the social aspects of participation within medical research.', 'Nicola Desmond', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nicola-desmond', '', '', '2020-03-30 09:15:13', '2020-03-30 09:15:13', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/?post_type=researchers&#038;p=45', 0, 'researchers', '', 0),
