(62, 1, '2020-01-20 14:23:30', '2020-01-20 14:23:30', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Although that was the main objective at that time, it became more evident<br>\nthat more was needed to be done. During this time, medical research in<br>\nMalawi was booming and the demand for meaningful engagement with<br>\nresearch communities was also increasing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In a quest to meet this demand and the requirements of our funders including Wellcome Trust, Malawi Liverpool Wellcome Trust (MLW) through it Science Communication department started to diversify its initiatives for public and community engagement. Science Communication therefore became an integral part of the research strategy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Public Engagement', '', 'private', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'public-engagement', '', '', '2020-03-10 09:45:09', '2020-03-10 09:45:09', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/?page_id=62', 0, 'page', '', 0),
