(293, 1, '2020-01-27 08:14:01', '2020-01-27 08:14:01', 'The Pathogen Biology Group seeks to understand the how pathogens come to, spread and evolve in Malawi and more broadly across Africa. We use this information to not only predict what might occur in the future so that preventative measures can begin early but also to guide the development of potential treatments.', 'Pathogen Biology Group', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pathogen-biology-group', '', '', '2020-03-23 07:37:06', '2020-03-23 07:37:06', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/?post_type=research&#038;p=293', 0, 'research', '', 0),
