(502, 1, '2020-03-11 11:11:57', '2020-03-11 11:11:57', 'Antony is a Clinical Officer within the Viral Immunology Group. He obtained a Diploma in in Clinical Medicine from Malamulo College of Health Sciences In 2006. He has vast experience in both clinical and field studies.\r\n\r\nCurrently, he is part of a study investigating the role of developmentally regulated microRNAs in neonatal immunity. His major interest is clinical research involving children. Antony’s long-term goal is to help the training of next generation of health workers in Malawi.', 'Antony Chipolopolo', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'antony-chipolopolo', '', '', '2020-03-11 11:11:57', '2020-03-11 11:11:57', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/?post_type=researchers&#038;p=502', 0, 'researchers', '', 0);
