(3041, 1, '2020-03-20 08:56:56', '2020-03-20 08:56:56', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">On 8 February 2019, MLW received three visitors from London School of Hygiene &amp; Tropical Medicine namely: Amit Bhasin, Ruth Lorimer and Rebecca Handley. Together with FIEBRE Study staff, they visited William Village, in the Traditional Authority of Katunga, where they went to study participant’s house to find out what she understands about the study and to see how people in the community perceive the FIEBRE study.</p>\n&nbsp;\n<p style=\"text-align: justify\">On arrival at the village, they were received by the village headwoman, the participant and her children. The meeting ended successfully with smiles and handshakes.</p>', 'FIEBRE in practice: Malawi FIEBRE visit to William village, TA Katunga', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1132-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-03-20 08:56:56', '2020-03-20 08:56:56', '', 1132, 'http://127.0.0.1/1132-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
