(3698, 1, '2020-09-15 08:12:47', '2020-09-15 08:12:47', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MLW is an internationally prominent\nhealth research institution led by Malawian &amp; International Scientists,\npursuing scientific excellence and improving the health of people in\nsub-Saharan Africa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MLW\nis built around excellent laboratories, strategically located in the largest\nhospital in Malawi, Queen Elizabeth Central Hospital. It is closely linked with\nthe community and is an integral part of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.medcol.mw/\">College of Medicine</a>. These relationships provide a unique opportunity replicated in few\ncentres in Africa to study major health issues spanning both community and\nhospital.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since\nits inception, MLW has maintained partnership with the Liverpool School of\nTropical Medicine, the University of Liverpool and the Wellcome Trust. MLW is\nbased in Blantyre with field research sites around urban Blantyre, Thyolo,\nChikhwawa, Zomba, Mangochi and Machinga.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Welcome', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-15 08:12:47', '2020-09-15 08:12:47', '', 7, 'http://127.0.0.1/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3699, 1, '2020-09-15 10:06:24', '2020-09-15 10:06:24', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our vision</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>MLW has a vision of science driving health and wellbeing in Malawi.&nbsp; This is bold, ambitious and challenging as Malawi is among the least developed economies in the world, with severe challenges related to population density, climate change and environmental degradation, nutrition, endemic diseases including HIV, TB and malaria, education and weak governmental infrastructure.&nbsp; MLW scientists have courage, commitment, energy and belief – with these combined with excellent funding, facilities and partnerships, we achieve great things.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our mission</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The MLW Mission is to conduct high quality research to improve health and to train the next generation of researchers.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Research is  nurtured in six Themes – </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/population-health/\">Population Health</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/social-sciences/\"> Social Sciences </a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/maternal-neonatal-and-child-health-theme/\">Maternal, Neonatal and Child Health,</a> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/vaccine-implementation-and-impact/\">Vaccines</a> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/clinical-and-experimental-medicine/\">Clinical and Experimental Medicine </a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1/theme/infection-biology/\"> Infection Biology. </a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These Themes catalyse the interactions between our 15 Research Groups, 6 Associate Research Groups and three Research Support Units.&nbsp; Themes are a natural transition from the previous two large programme aims which were (1) To prevent deaths in hospital and (2) to prevent disease in the community.&nbsp; The change has been driven by growth, diversity and the ideas generated by a new generation of leaders.&nbsp; Training in MLW is from junior scientist to Group Head and from operations staff recruit to Department Head. Nine of the Research Group Heads as well as the Director were previously trainees at MLW</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>2020 Annual Group Reports</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This document describes the success, current activity and plans of the Research Groups at MLW.&nbsp; It seeks to be informative and inspirational, both for junior scientists who might choose how to join MLW, for seniors and for collaborators.&nbsp; I hope you enjoy it as much as I do.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Best wishes</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-15 10:06:24', '2020-09-15 10:06:24', '', 9, 'http://127.0.0.1/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
